data.description: Impressive townhome in the sought-after Countryshire neighborhood! This 2 BD, 2 BA home has a MAIN FLOOR MASTER, 11 ft clngs w/vaults and a 1 car garage. You will be wowed by the tall clngs, large windows and smart living space in this home! The ext has brick, vinyl siding and a front porch w/vinyl railing. Features inc 42 inch cabinets, washer-dryer-refrig-stove-micro-D/W, tile b-splash, open floor plan, dbl bowl vanity in the Mstr Bath, 11 ft clngs in the Master Bdr, W/I closet, main flr laundry, deck, Nest thermostat, new HVAC in 2023, ceilings fan and more. The upstairs has a spacious Loft, bdr and full bath. The LL has a R/I bath, egress window and walkout for an easy future finish. Residents will enjoy neighborhood amenities w/a pool, bath house, sports courts-pickleball-tennis, playground, lake and green space. A reasonable monthly fee covers lawn, landscape, snow removal (per Ind), roof maint, ext maint, and some insurance. Desirable Wentzville schools, so much to love!
